data.description: Step into comfort and make this spacious, meticulously cared-for single-family home featuring an inviting above-ground pool in the enchanting Poinciana community your own. The moment you enter, a welcoming family room beckons, creating a cozy haven for both intimate gatherings and lively moments with family and friends.Boasting 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, this residence is an ideal sanctuary for families or those who love to host. Picture yourself basking in the Florida sunshine within your private backyard oasis—a haven for gardening, barbecues, or simply unwinding after a bustling day.For those with vehicles, the convenience of a two-car garage ensures ample parking space and offers additional storage options to keep your belongings organized. Beyond the comforts of home, this residence is strategically positioned, providing easy access to the myriad shopping, dining, and entertainment options that Poinciana has to offer. Embrace a lifestyle of comfort and convenience in this exceptional Poinciana gem.
